name: Pink Dichroic Glass Gem on “Josephine” Celtic Leather Bracelet w/ Sterling Silver
description:
Pink dichroic glass boxes and Pink dichroic glass is fused over a 19mm x 15mm oval of opaque pink glass. The 5/8” wide, 7 ½ long bracelet is made with one 5’ 2mm black leather cord woven into a Celtic “Josephine” knotted pattern and finished with sterling silver wire, 5mm sterling silver jump rings, and a 10mm sterling silver toggle closure.
Originally $35.

name: Green Dichroic Glass Starred Gem on Rectangular Celtic Leather Bracelet w/ Sterling Silver
description:
Green and gold dichroic glass dots are fused over green dichroic glass on a 15mm x 12mm oval of white glass. The ½” wide, 7” long bracelet is made with a single 5’ long 2mm strand of black leather that is folded and woven into a rectangular Celtic knot pattern and finished with sterling silver wire, 5mm sterling silver jump rings, and a 10mm sterling silver toggle closure. 
Originally $42.

name: Gold Dichroic, Red & Yellow Glass “4 Square” on Celtic Leather Bracelet w/ Sterling Silver.
description:
Gold patterned dichroic glass is fused into opaque red glass in a four square pattern with a pale blue dichroic glass center over opaque yellow glass on a 35mm X 30mm rectangle of translucent red glass. The 7” long 1” wide bracelet is made with two 6’ long 2mm cords of black leather woven into a continuous rectangular Celtic rectangular knot pattern and finished with sterling silver wire, 5mm sterling silver jump rings, and a 10mm sterling silver toggle closure. 
Originally $65.

name: Purple, Teal & Silver Dichroic Glass “Starflower” on Celtic Leather Bracelet w/ Sterling Silver
description:
Purple and teal dichroic glass creates the “Starflower” layered over silver dichroic glass with orange glass flower accents that is then fused over a 1.5” circle of translucent purple glass. The 7” long 1” wide bracelet is made with two 6’ long  2mm cords of black leather woven into a continuous rectangular Celtic rectangular knot pattern and finished with sterling silver wire, 5mm sterling silver jump rings, and a 10mm sterling silver toggle closure.
Originally $95.

name: Gold Dichroic Glass and Multi Colored Jasper Beaded Bracelet
description:
#100-3115: Layered dichroic glass in gold and pink and 4 mm mixed jasper beads are woven into a fun bracelet with golden 19 strand Beadalon beading wire and a gold colored vintage box clasp. The dichroic glass gem is an oval that is 7/8” long by 6/8” wide and backed in black glass. The bracelet is 7 1/8” around. 
Originally $48.
